metadata.name: Midnight in Tokyo
metadata.description:
Walking the streets of Tokyo at midnight. Alone with my thoughts. An intimate date with the city I love.

I walked these empty streets. Along my travels I stop to replenish. These late hours call for coffee. An unending task to explore this vast city.

The more I observe the fragments of this city, the more I come to love them. I may be finding my foothold I need to go on living.
